ii20er.Job Description:
Coast Mountain Hydro

Functional Responsibility
Reporting to the Plant Manager, while acting under the guidance of on-site Management, the student will work with the CMH Maximo project team to obtain necessary asset, material, and maintenance task data.

Principal Responsibilities
Obtain data from physical inspection and photographs of the CMH assets and materials, review of drawings and manufacturers manuals, and discussions with CMH team members from various trades and backgrounds;
Work in the Maximo computerized inventory management system to input data as directed;
On-the-job and Safety training will be provided on site at the commencement of the assignment;
Assist Maximo project team with other tasks as required.
May be assigned to alternative tasks to support the operation as needed.
